Cryptocurrency trading carries substantial risk. Leveraged perpetual contracts
in particular can result in losses exceeding your initial deposit.

By using this software you acknowledge that:
  - The author(s) are not responsible for any financial losses you may incur.
  - You will independently verify any trading decision before risking capital.
